## Requirements:

# polybar
https://github.com/polybar/polybar

# compton
https://github.com/chjj/compton

# xwinwrap
https://github.com/ujjwal96/xwinwrap

# mpv
https://mpv.io/

# mpc
https://github.com/MusicPlayerDaemon/mpc

# mpd
https://github.com/MusicPlayerDaemon/MPD

## Fonts

# Font Awesome
https://fontawesome.com/

# Luculent
http://eastfarthing.com/luculent/

## Installation:

mkdir ~/.config/leftwm/themes/watercolors
cp -R ./watercolors ~/.config/leftwm/themes/watercolors
ln -s ~/.config/leftwm/themes/watercolors ~/.config/leftwm/themes/current
mv ~/.Xresources ~/.Xresources.old
pkill leftwm-worker
